Fiends torment, no CHRISTIANS thirſt for Gold.
TO 'BE, Contents his natural Deſire,
He aſks no Angels Wing, no Seraphs Fire;
But thinks, admitted to that equal SKY,
His FAITHFUL DOG ſhall bear him Company.
